&lt;p&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/SOLR-6342&quot; title=&quot;Solr should mention CHANGES from Lucene which have side effects in Solr&quot; class=&quot;issue-link&quot; data-issue-key=&quot;SOLR-6342&quot;&gt;&lt;del&gt;SOLR-6342&lt;/del&gt;&lt;/a&gt;: build.xml clones lucene/CHANGES.txt as LUCENE_CHANGES.txt in solr releases; changes2html hotlinks LUCENE_CHANGES.txt when found (merge r1618281)&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
                            <comment id="14099217" author="hossman" created="Fri, 15 Aug 2014 21:49:46 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;Committed on sarowe&apos;s behalf per IRC disucssion.&lt;/p&gt;

